## Suggested Fix

Validate input before parsing:

```java
private String unescapeEntity(String e) {
    if (e.charAt(0) == '#') {
        String numStr;
        int radix;
        if (e.length() > 1 && (e.charAt(1) == 'x' || e.charAt(1) == 'X')) {
            numStr = e.substring(2);
            radix = 16;
        } else {
            numStr = e.substring(1);
            radix = 10;
        }
        // Validate before parsing
        if (numStr.isEmpty() || !numStr.chars().allMatch(c -> Character.digit(c, radix) >= 0)) {
            return "";  // or throw JSONException
        }
        cp = Integer.parseInt(numStr, radix);
    }
    // ...
}
```

